Title: Non-Renormalisation Theorems in Global Supersymmetry

Comments: 13 pages LaTeX2e

Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys.Proc.Suppl. 101 (2001) 99-106

We review the history of non-renormalisation theorems in globalsupersymmetry, as well as their importance in all attempts to applysupersymmetry to the real world.